ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend this course to other students only if it is more organized in the future. Four instructors did not work,
All students that have some interest in development should take it.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It helps me learn various research topics.

This class itself was definitely usesful for exposing me to topics in development and how modern development economists approach some of my topics of interest. The most useful part of the coure was the reading list: each instructor assigned a big batch of very useful papers.
As I am following development as one of my fields this course was really helpful giving me a broad and deeper idea of some current and past work in the field.
